      "ai_prompt": "Wide exterior view of the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant at dawn, the massive reactor building and cooling towers silhouetted against a pale sky washed in cold grey-blue light. The plant stands immense and industrial on the flat Ukrainian steppe, cooling towers venting faint wisps of steam into the still morning air — vast, foreboding, and eerily quiet.",
      "ai_prompt_variations": [
        "Extreme-wide aerial perspective of the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant complex at early dawn, the entire facility spread across a treeless plain under an overcast sky. The reactor buildings appear small against the enormous grey expanse of sky and flat land, emphasising the isolation of the site.",
        "Ground-level exterior shot of the Chernobyl plant at dawn from across a cooling pond, the reactor building and chimney stacks reflected in the still dark water. Warm first light catching only the tops of the structures while the lower plant remains in cold shadow.",
        "Tight telephoto compression of the Chernobyl cooling tower at dawn under overcast clouds pressing down behind the concrete hyperboloid structure. Steam billowing from the tower top disperses into the grey sky, almost monochromatic, no saturation.",
